Author: nodfvther
Text: you’re absolutely right, I think it was just that “lack of control” that shook me at first.  Sorry to hear about your binge, today is a new day.

Author: wheresmywinegums
Text: Honey I know you feel bad, but if it makes you feel better, 500 cals is my normal breakfast... yesterday I binged ~5000 cals. It could be much worse.
